Output demo/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1600
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set TypingSpeed 80ms

Hide
Type "cd /Users/currenjin/Documents/personal/repositories/crewalk && ./crewalk --demo"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

